  "title": "Quantity Surveyor",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Prepare and manage project cost estimates, budgets, and cash flow</p></li><li><p>Handle progress claims, interim valuations, and final accounts</p></li><li><p>Monitor project costs and ensure expenditures remain within budget</p></li><li><p>Evaluate variations, claims, and subcontractor payments</p></li><li><p>Prepare and review contracts, subcontracts, and related documentation</p></li><li><p>Liaise with project managers, site teams, consultants, and clients</p></li><li><p>Track project progress and report on cost performance</p></li><li><p>Assist in procurement and subcontractor coordination</p></li><li><p>Ensure compliance with contractual and company requirements</p></li></ul><p><strong>Requirement:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Diploma or Degree in Quantity Surveying or related field</p></li><li><p>Minimum 2–5 years of relevant working experience in construction</p></li></ul><p><br /><strong>HOW TO APPLY:</strong></p><p>Interested applicants, kindly send your resume in MS WORD format or please click on “Apply Now”.</p><p>We regret only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p><p>Important Note: Trust Recruit Pte Ltd is committed to safeguarding your personal data in accordance with the Personal Data Protection Act (PDPA).</p><p>Please read our privacy statement on our corporate website.</p><p>Trust Recruit Pte Ltd</p><p>EA License No: 19C9950</p><p>EA Personnel: Tan Sin Yong (Stella)</p><p>EA Personnel Reg No: R24124127</p>",
